jmccarty@spd.dsccc.com (Mike McCarty) writes:

> Actually, one can export DES only by transporting hardware. The
> standard itself specifically says that software implementations
> of the algorithm are not DES compliant.

For that matter, there is no DES standard anymore.  So
is no such thing as certifiable hardware DES, either.

